oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Map of Rutherford County, Tenn. : from actual surveys
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The map shows roads, railroads, property tract lines, tract numbers, and landowners' names. This map is mentioned numerous times in Louise Houck Wiser’s book, A History of Rutherford County Schools (Murfreesboro, Tenn.: Rutherford County Retired Teachers Association, 1986).
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Real property--Tennessee--Rutherford County--Maps; Landowners--Tennessee--Rutherford County--Maps
oai_dc:dc.dc:format: 1 map on 4 sheets : col., cloth backing ; 135 x 96 cm.. on sheets 72 x 50 cm.
oai_dc:dc.dc:publisher: Digital Initiatives, James E. Walker Library, Middle Tennessee State University
